---
title: Quick Teriyaki Beef & Noodles with Roasted Nuts & Lime
description: Sometimes you can’t go past the classics, like this beef stir-fry with a sweet and savoury sauce. With flat noodles and colourful
veggies, it tastes like a takeaway delight, but with the satisfaction of making it yourself!

*Keep an eye out... Due to recent sourcing challenges, we’ve replaced courgette with capsicum and lemon with lime, which may be a little different to what’s pictured. Don’t worry, your recipe will be just as delicious!*
